text:
Ugh... I'm hungry...
Um... Can we go to the convenience store...?

...?
Oh no... Was it a bad idea...?

It's not that, though...!
...Tenka-chan... Winter at the convenience store...

The fluffy steamed buns,
and the warm oden...
You just can't resist reaching out...

Welcome! Currently, we're having a special discount
on steamed buns and oden!
